   20: -module(binary_property_test_SUITE).
   21: 
   22: -compile([export_all, nowarn_export_all]).
   23: 
   24: all() ->
   25:     [{group, valid_input}, {group, invalid_input}].
   26: 
   27: valid_input_tests() ->
   28:     [at_case,
   29:      bin_to_list_1_case, bin_to_list_2_3_case,
   30:      compile_pattern_case,
   31:      copy_case,
   32:      decode_hex_case,
   33:      decode_unsigned_case,
   34:      encode_hex_case,
   35:      encode_unsigned_case,
   36:      first_case,
   37:      last_case,
   38:      list_to_bin_case,
   39:      longest_common_prefix_case,
   40:      longest_common_suffix_case,
   41:      match_case,
   42:      matches_case,
   43:      part_case,
   44:      replace_case,
   45:      split_case].
   46: 
   47: out_of_binary_tests() ->
   48:     [at_invalid_index_case,
   49:      bin_to_list_2_3_invalid_range_case,
   50:      match_3_invalid_scope_case,
   51:      matches_3_invalid_scope_case,
   52:      part_invalid_range_case,
   53:      replace_4_invalid_scope_case, replace_4_invalid_insert_replaced_case,
   54:      split_3_invalid_scope_case].
   55: 
   56: invalid_subject_tests() ->
   57:     [at_invalid_subject_case,
   58:      bin_to_list_invalid_subject_case,
   59:      copy_invalid_subject_case,
   60:      decode_hex_invalid_subject_case,
   61:      decode_unsigned_invalid_subject_case,
   62:      encode_hex_invalid_subject_case,
   63:      first_invalid_subject_case,
   64:      last_invalid_subject_case,
   65:      longest_common_prefix_invalid_subject_case,
   66:      longest_common_suffix_invalid_subject_case,
   67:      match_invalid_subject_case,
   68:      matches_invalid_subject_case,
   69:      part_invalid_subject_case,
   70:      replace_invalid_subject_case,
   71:      split_invalid_subject_case].
   72: 
   73: invalid_pattern_tests() ->
   74:     [compile_pattern_invalid_pattern_case,
   75:      match_invalid_pattern_case,
   76:      matches_invalid_pattern_case,
   77:      replace_invalid_pattern_case,
   78:      split_invalid_pattern_case].
   79: 
   80: misc_invalid_input_tests() ->
   81:     [copy_2_invalid_n_case,
   82:      decode_hex_invalid_chars_case,
   83:      decode_unsigned_2_invalid_endianness_case,
   84:      encode_hex_2_invalid_case_case,
   85:      encode_unsigned_invalid_integer_case,
   86:      encode_unsigned_2_invalid_endianness_case,
   87:      list_to_bin_invalid_bytes_case,
   88:      replace_invalid_replacement_case].
   89: 
   90: groups() ->
   91:     [{valid_input, [], valid_input_tests()},
   92:      {invalid_input, [], [{out_of_binary, [], out_of_binary_tests()},
   93:                           {invalid_subjects, [], invalid_subject_tests()},
   94:                           {invalid_patterns, [], invalid_pattern_tests()},
   95:                           {misc_invalid, [], misc_invalid_input_tests()}]}].
   96: 
   97: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   98:     ct_property_test:init_per_suite(Config).
   99: 
  100: end_per_suite(Config) ->
  101:     Config.
  102: 
  103: do_proptest(Prop, Config) ->
  104:     ct_property_test:quickcheck(binary_prop:Prop(), Config).
  105:
